{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175920/extras/Ads\u0131z_tasar\u0131m.gif?t=1737561987\" /><br><strong>NOIR BUNKER is an isometric pixel art puzzle-thriller set in a tense, atmospheric world. Navigate the cold, foggy depths of a dark bunker, where every choice you make can either save or doom you.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175920/extras/Ads\u0131z_tasar\u0131m2.gif?t=1737561987\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175920/extras/Ads\u0131z_tasar\u01313.gif?t=1737561987\" /><br><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>TWO DISTINCT CONTROL SYSTEMS. Experience the game through either Tank Controls for strategic, fixed-camera precision or Free Camera Controls for a broader, dynamic exploration.<br><br></li><li>PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR AND INTENSE PUZZLES. Unravel the dark mysteries hidden within the bunker\u2019s eerie corridors, where every shadow conceals a riddle, and each decision demands a sacrifice.<br><br></li><li>IMMERSIVE NOIR VISUALS. Dive into a world of stunning pixel art with a noir aesthetic, designed to draw you deeper into its unsettling atmosphere.<br><br></li><li>STRATEGIC OBJECT INTERACTIONS. Simple objects like a chair become pivotal; will it be your refuge or the key to deeper despair? Every interaction has consequences.<br><br></li><li>DYNAMIC CAMERA ANGLES. Switch between fixed and free camera perspectives, each offering unique challenges and intensifying the game\u2019s tension.<br><br></li><li>DARK AND ATMOSPHERIC SETTING. Explore a meticulously crafted bunker where every corner, every room is filled with a sense of dread, and where every action carries a heavy cost.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737561987